 "title": "Masquerade Ball: A Night on Yavin (Part 3)",
 "summary": "At the climax of the masquerade aboard the Angry Rancor, hostess Inanna and her sister Sel run the costume contest from the stage. After voting, Ramyxth the totem spirit and the masked Doctor Lepidoptera are announced as the winners and called up to collect their prizes of casino chips and hotel vouchers. Around the bar the banter continues: the drunken pirate Juran fights with his helmet, Kyrin Sh'vani offers Ka'una patient dance instruction, and the enigmatic old-Republic-styled Rasi trades barbs with the doctor. Identities continue to be teased and guessed at as the party rolls on.",
